{"tid":5250,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，係咪要幫LIHKG做下宣傳先有得玩落去","createTime":"2016-11-26T20:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:22:15.000Z","uid":17232,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e059392963f8df4d7c1a273fec0845d0bd49c242","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:05:28.000Z","msg":"始終街外人個個都淨係知高登呢樣野。可能有啲初中雞啱啱升高中想睇下咩叫高登，都只會係playstore serch 香港高登，或者google高登。根本唔會知Lihkg咩黎。時代不斷更替，上高登既唔係永遠都係我地呢班人。咁樣長遠黎講Lihkg好難夠高登玩。<br />\n<br />\n就好似我2011年加入高登，根本唔知膠登係咩黎。當年高登大屠殺之後夠有好多人遷移去高登啦。最後一班新高登仔淨係對高登有歸屬感，邊有人會上膠登吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔夠幾年班膠登會員一樣頂唔順回流高登。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以要o係歷史吸取教訓，我覺得唯一解決到呢個問題既方法就只有宣傳。吸撚埋所有有心加入高登既一份子同埋潛在高登仔過黎，咁先徹徹底底取代高登！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d821a38a276e6fb56533d0873177871abd3d7916","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:07:35.000Z","msg":"屌深夜都咁多人，好難睇到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09466513d27ad24297e860f4f1060549c9777549","tid":5250,"uid":11009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:08:35.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f40eca57e611e1b36dede8a938531914c564804","tid":5250,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"認同，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f09b7cc19a9783837e2a132e137daa72fa35e","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:13:17.000Z","msg":"隔離舊登仲話咩理性分析LIHKG不能取代高登的三個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就理性分析喇，仲要及時預知再搵解決方法"},{"pid":"73ea50f8b4550d939c7275e464956cefbaacb627","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:17:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fb6dbcb5a0b34bceacf700d8544caf3cb3d2a91","tid":5250,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:31:48.000Z","msg":"Push1push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297466b1401417e578851e5d4b7ec18e1ddc08cb","tid":5250,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:32:21.000Z","msg":"宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6000b85fb0d8e0d3dfd4f4bcf40884ad8efdc7","tid":5250,"uid":9520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:33:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb3a70a44ddd3ec7a0dd4d0d0e53b69c71e4266","tid":5250,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:35:20.000Z","msg":"同高登齊名既梗係黃金"},{"pid":"cb10fb5c7cf861add8535f6e2f77a0507791967a","tid":5250,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:36:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以簡化個名<br />\n好難up出口"},{"pid":"438413ed3c25a399e4683528841135ce21055115","tid":5250,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94409ba8d6c145b066964c59787d9a66873585f2","tid":5250,"uid":6631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:37:59.000Z","msg":"仲叫自己高登仔咁係人都去左高登先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e42bf73e59f8e76757875c21963f33ee7936127","tid":5250,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b83cdbbcf2b2af2a9a296dab3fcec73c32323f8","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg&h=288053b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\napple 免費宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗啲人見到一個高登，一個lihkg討論區。一定係下載高登嗰個。佢地根本唔會知lihkg係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b64fd4dad3ad67a9654fa79fdbe18296227a37","tid":5250,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg&h=288053b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\napple 免費宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官方app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7659ca7c732aa55ff1fef3872dcd31eaf2338633","tid":5250,"uid":8798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:39:37.000Z","msg":"我反而唔知點解膠登點解搞唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b082c787950883886dbb545c39c659780637eb30","tid":5250,"uid":6311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:40:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0e38cd8c56cd64526101bf0ef994ad4896e54e0","tid":5250,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲叫自己高登仔咁係人都去左高登先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我諗要幫lihkg改個順口既中文名。講真，lihkg呢個名已經開衰左個頭，又唔知點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ab12e983a29fb8742abfc6825c66e0b6ff20c3","tid":5250,"uid":1686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F043547_00a9a8f5dc1401cc259b2ee07aa6ce59.jpg&h=288053b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\napple 免費宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c82fa8d7506b50187753870b25e1e46e69456d0","tid":5250,"uid":16522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:40:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63bb6f2dcc99ae6ef2a7f4b8405b3d2f4d65da13","tid":5250,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而唔知點解膠登點解搞唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始其實好好<br />\n後期換咗admin 同有班串過馬撚既人<br />\n當然仲有好多因素 本身有心攪嘅兄弟俾人屌走晒<br />\n想知詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgalden.com/view/392100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgalden.com%2Fview%2F392100&d=0F%2F3G%2BKy%2F4cf3VPMUpUJ2cW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=3c88129c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgalden.com/view/392100</a>"},{"pid":"cb357f87a848a4b02dd54db63395db776778c7ec","tid":5250,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:44:04.000Z","msg":"Btw 613之後我無返過去<br />\n我由屌佢嗰一日屌佢開始就講咗唔會返去"},{"pid":"c2c633ae56faff6d29a2a5d7836a308873ac703e","tid":5250,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 613之後我無返過去<br />\n我由屌佢嗰一日開始就講咗唔會返去</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c7ad201d931ef2120b8516fd9f1e268281d11922","tid":5250,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"去高登個facebook宣傳咪得"}]}